ğŸ› ï¸ Installation
Option 1: Using Docker (Recommended)
This is the fastest way to get your bot running in a production-ready environment.

Clone the repository:

Bash

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/your-repo-name.git
cd your-repo-name
Build and run the container:

Bash

docker build -t telegram-downloader-bot .
docker run -d --name downloader-bot -e BOT_TOKEN="your_token_here" telegram-downloader-bot
Option 2: Local Setup
Install dependencies:

Bash

pip install -r requirements.txt
Configure environment: Replace the BOT_TOKEN in downloader_bot.py with your actual token.

Run the bot:

Bash

python downloader_bot.py
ğŸš€ Usage
Start the bot by sending the /start command.

Paste any video URL from a supported website.

The bot will analyze the link, download the best quality available, and send the file directly to your chat.

